commit.message:
update tests

- minor re-work on tests/smoke-test.py to allow it to be run from within tests folder OR parent
- added vf_test.py to exercise Variable Font methods

Add Variable Font example

- add hello-vf.py which generates a simple image using a variable font
- add SourceSansVariable-Roman.otf font & License file for same

Add/extend Variable Font support

- add related Structures in ft_structs.py
- link up backend FreeType methods in raw.py
- extend Face class with VF support and related utility functions

Update .gitignore

add *.eggs
